arStrings.szText: Father Inarius, as I shed my wicked blood, let it be purified in thy Light. Let the Light fill the darkness within all of us.
Solemn. You are conducting a magic ritual and the words are important to get right.
Ô Père Inarius, purifiez de votre Lumière le sang vicié que je verse aujourd’hui. Inondez de votre Lumière les ténèbres qui nous entourent.
